<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(١٨٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الظُّلَّةِ}</span> ... سَحَابَةٍ أَظَلَّتْهُمْ وَجَدُوا تَحْتَهَا بَرْدًا، فَلمَّا اجْتَمَعُوا أَحْرَقَتْهُمْ بِنَارِهَا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١٩٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الرُّوحُ الْأَمِينُ}</span> ... جِبْرِيلُ - عليه السلام -.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٩٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زُبُرِ الْأَوَّلِينَ}</span> ... كُتُبِ الأَنْبِيَاءِ السَّابِقِينَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٩٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{آيَةً}</span> ... عَلَامَةً عَلَى صِحَّةِ نُبُوَّتِكَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١٩٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْأَعْجَمِينَ}</span> ... الَّذِينَ لَا يَتَكَلَّمُونَ العَرَبِيَّةَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَلَكْنَاهُ}</span> ... أَدْخَلْنَا التَّكْذِيبَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَغْتَةً}</span> ... فَجْأَةً.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُنظَرُونَ}</span> ... مُمْهَلُونَ مُؤَخَّرُونَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَفَرَأَيْتَ}</span> ... أَفَعَلِمْتَ؟<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٢١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{السَّمْعِ}</span> ... اسْتِمَاعِ القُرْآنِ مِنَ السَّمَاءِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٢١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَمَعْزُولُونَ}</span> ... لَمَحْجُوبُونَ مَرْجُومُونَ بِالشُّهُبِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٢١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَاخْفِضْ جَنَاحَكَ}</span> ... أَلِنْ جَانِبَكَ وَكَلامَكَ تَوَاضُعًا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٢١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حِينَ تَقُومُ}</span> ... تُصَلِّي اللَّيْلَ وَحْدَكَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
